BattleShip is a two player board game. This game contains one board (10x10 blocks) for each player.
The boards represents the ocean and we have to place our ships in the ocean without showing it to other player. 

After placing the ships both players hit the blocks on opponent's board in alternate moves. When a player hit a block which contains the ship then it will be a hit and he will one more chance to hit the board.


The player who will first destroy all the ships of other player, will be the winner.

Now in this program one player is computer and it will use the AI to play it's move.
